document_api_meta.title: Confirm Package Shipment
document_api_meta.env_desc: This API enables a warehouse service provider to send package shipment information for an order. Only warehouse service providers who have been certified by the platform have permission to access this interface.

request_header_param.name: x-tts-access-token
request_header_param.desc:
Depends on the auth type of the API. 
1. The seller access_token value from [Get Access Token](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/678e3a3292b0f40314a92d75#Get%20Access%20Token%20API), when user_type = 0. Follow this [guide](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/678e3a344ddec3030b238fa0) to get seller access_token.
2. The creator access_token value from [Get Access Token](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/678e3a3292b0f40314a92d75#Get%20Access%20Token%20API), when user_type = 1. Follow this [guide](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/678e3a362dccb8030ea6f98c) to get creator access_token.
3. The partner access_token value from [Get Access Token](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/678e3a3292b0f40314a92d75#Get%20Access%20Token%20API), when user_type = 3. Follow this [guide](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/678e3a3978f4c20311b8b555) to get partner access_token.

request_query_param.name: app_key
request_query_param.desc: Every single app will have a unique key. Please use the specific key assigned to your app.

request_query_param.name: sign
request_query_param.desc: Signature generated by gen algorithm. When you send API requests to TTS, you must sign them so that TTS can identify the senders.

request_query_param.name: timestamp
request_query_param.desc: Unix timestamp GMT (UTC+00:00). This timestamp is used across all API requests. Developers can use this convert to local time.

request_body_param.name: warehouse_provider_id
request_body_param.desc: Warehouse provider ID, unique and provided by TikTok

request_body_param.name: ^shipping_origin_city
request_body_param.desc: Origin city name for the shipment

request_body_param.name: ^ship_time_millis
request_body_param.desc: Time when the order is shipped out of the warehouse (Unix timestamp in milliseconds)

request_body_param.name: ^create_time_millis
request_body_param.desc: Time when warehouse receives the order (Unix timestamp in milliseconds)

request_body_param.name: ^handover_time_millis
request_body_param.desc: Time when the order is handed over to the shipping provider (Unix timestamp in milliseconds)

request_body_param.name: ^^unit
request_body_param.desc:
Package dimension unit
Possible values:
- METER
- CENTIMETER
- MILLIMETER
- MICRON
- FOOT
- INCH

request_body_param.name: ^^unit
request_body_param.desc:
Package weight unit
Possible values:
- KILOGRAM
- GRAM
- MILLIGRAM
- POUND
- OUNCE

request_body_param.name: ^tcw_warehouse_type
request_body_param.desc:
TikTok warehouse type 
Possible values:
- STANDARD: Standard warehouse that has not been specifically certified by TikTok 
- TIKTOK_CERTIFIED_WAREHOUSE_FULFILLMENT: TikTok certified warehouse usually offering better service levels. Certified warehouses are required to meet fulfillment timeline standards set by TikTok

response_param.name: code
response_param.desc: The success or failure status code returned in API response.

response_param.name: message
response_param.desc: The success or failure messages returned in API response. Reasons of failure will be described in the message.

response_param.name: ^success_packages
response_param.desc: List of packages that have been successfully confirmed

response_param.name: ^^message
response_param.example: Provider is not supported by TikTok Shop

error_code_list.msg: provider is not in package information send-back  white list
package param  invalid, please check detail fail reason
